beer.beer_description:
Help Wanted


Beer Description Wordsmith


We are looking for a dynamic, collaborative, motivated, lateral thinker to join our small team. A position is available writing descriptions for new beers, generally New England IPA’s and Oat Cream IPA’s. You will be required to write at least 2 new labels per week. Applicants will be proficient in writing buzzwords such as pillowy, tropical, citrus, smooth, mouthfeel and juicy. Please find example provided: Flavour Generator is full of juicy tropical fruit notes and has a pillowy mouthfeel.


If this sounds like you, please send your CV, a headshot, your original description for Flavour Generator and 4 Mountain Culture barcodes to:


Mountain Culture

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 305 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%.  Try 5 more for Level 62!
